CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_fake_nomes_sexo_id
ON ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes (sexo, id);

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION ${SCHEMA}.anonimizar(
    p_nome TEXT,
    p_anonimizar BOOLEAN,
    p_sexo CHAR(1) DEFAULT NULL
)
RETURNS TEXT
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $anon$
DECLARE
    v_nome TEXT;
    v_max_id BIGINT;
    v_id BIGINT;
BEGIN
    IF p_anonimizar IS FALSE THEN
        RETURN p_nome;
    END IF;

    IF p_sexo IS NOT NULL THEN
        SELECT max(id) INTO v_max_id
        FROM ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes
        WHERE sexo = p_sexo;

        IF v_max_id IS NULL THEN
            RETURN p_nome;
        END IF;

        v_id := 1 + floor(random() * v_max_id)::bigint;

        SELECT nome_completo INTO v_nome
        FROM ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes
        WHERE sexo = p_sexo
          AND id >= v_id
        ORDER BY id
        LIMIT 1;

        IF v_nome IS NULL THEN
            SELECT nome_completo INTO v_nome
            FROM ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes
            WHERE sexo = p_sexo
            ORDER BY id
            LIMIT 1;
        END IF;

    ELSE
        SELECT max(id) INTO v_max_id
        FROM ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes;

        IF v_max_id IS NULL THEN
            RETURN p_nome;
        END IF;

        v_id := 1 + floor(random() * v_max_id)::bigint;

        SELECT nome_completo INTO v_nome
        FROM ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes
        WHERE id >= v_id
        ORDER BY id
        LIMIT 1;

        IF v_nome IS NULL THEN
            SELECT nome_completo INTO v_nome
            FROM ${SCHEMA}.fake_nomes
            ORDER BY id
            LIMIT 1;
        END IF;
    END IF;

    RETURN COALESCE(v_nome, p_nome);
END;
$anon$;

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION ${SCHEMA}.gerar_cpf()
RETURNS TEXT
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $cpf$
DECLARE
    n1 INT; n2 INT; n3 INT; n4 INT; n5 INT;
    n6 INT; n7 INT; n8 INT; n9 INT;
    d1 INT; d2 INT;
    soma INT;
BEGIN
    n1 := floor(random() * 10);
    n2 := floor(random() * 10);
    n3 := floor(random() * 10);
    n4 := floor(random() * 10);
    n5 := floor(random() * 10);
    n6 := floor(random() * 10);
    n7 := floor(random() * 10);
    n8 := floor(random() * 10);
    n9 := floor(random() * 10);

    soma :=
        n1*10 + n2*9 + n3*8 + n4*7 + n5*6 +
        n6*5  + n7*4 + n8*3 + n9*2;

    d1 := 11 - (soma % 11);
    IF d1 >= 10 THEN d1 := 0; END IF;

    soma :=
        n1*11 + n2*10 + n3*9 + n4*8 + n5*7 +
        n6*6  + n7*5  + n8*4 + n9*3 + d1*2;

    d2 := 11 - (soma % 11);
    IF d2 >= 10 THEN d2 := 0; END IF;

    RETURN n1::TEXT || n2 || n3 || n4 || n5 ||
           n6 || n7 || n8 || n9 || d1 || d2;
END;
$cpf$;

documento_identificacao = ${SCHEMA}.gerar_cpf();
